Author: birake
Title: [ANN][TOKEN SALE] Birake.com - White Label Cryptocurrency Exchange
Body: What is BIRAKE- White Label Exchange?  The terms white label or private label are similar. White labeling is when a product or service removes their brand and logo from the end product and instead uses the branding requested by the purchaser.  Accoring to wikipedia definition “A white label product is a product or service produced by one company (the producer) that other companies (the marketers) rebrand to make it appear as if they had made it.”  “White Labeling” is found in supermarkets, consumer products, generic product including electornics and software packeges. For example in a supermarket you can buy all sorts of products that are sold under their brand, in the electronics industry the same model ca be sold by two or more companyes, under the brand used exclusivly by those companies.  Birake wants to bring this model into the blockchain network. The purpose is to create the largest crypto exchange on the blockchain and enable community members to create their own exchanges.  The main ideea behind Birake is to create a decentralized crypto exchange network where the community can trade currencies back and forth, sharing orders across all these exchanges.  With Birake everyone can have their OWN EXCHANGE PLATFORM. All the exchanges using the platform will share their orders meaning a new exchange client in the Birake platform will have many buy and sell orders from the first day launching of your own exchange.  In the Birake Platform, aspiring exchange owners can start right away from day 1! Future owners won’t face marketing problems and will save a lot of funds doing so. Birake offers the first of its kind and will revolutionize the individuality of the exchanges of today.
